---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SectionHeading from '../components/SectionHeading.astro';
import backgroundImage from '../assets/our-story-bg.jpeg';



// Founder images
const campusImage = "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1541339907198-e08756dedf3f?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1740&q=80";

---

<Layout title="About Us">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative h-[70vh] overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-black/70 to-black/50 z-10"></div>
    <img src={backgroundImage.src} alt="" fetchpriority="high" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"

    >
    
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-20 flex items-center">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 font-display leading-tight">
            Our Story
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-cream-light leading-relaxed">
            From a student's vision at the Air Force Institute of Technology to a movement transforming Africa's relationship with plastics.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Origin Story Section -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <SectionHeading 
            title="The Birth of Terra Verte Afrika" 
            subtitle="How a personal journey became a continental movement"
          />
          
          <div class="prose prose-lg prose-green">
            <p>
              Terra Verte Afrika began in the halls of the Air Force Institute of Technology, where I witnessed firsthand the overwhelming presence of plastic waste on our campus. As an Unversity engineering student, I was struck by the disconnect between our academic discussions of sustainability and the reality of our daily practices.
            </p>
            
            <p>
              The name "Terra Verte Afrika" combines Latin and Swahili influences - "Terra Verte" meaning "Green Earth" and "Afrika" representing our continent's unique spelling - symbolizing our commitment to blend traditional African wisdom with modern environmental solutions.
            </p>
            
            <blockquote class="italic text-green-dark border-l-4 border-green pl-4 my-6">
              "What started as a campus cleanup initiative has grown into a movement that's transforming how Africa thinks about plastic waste."
            </blockquote>
            
            <p>
              My university education opened my eyes to the scientific reality of plastic pollution, but it was the daily sight of plastic-choked drainage systems during rainy seasons that truly catalyzed action. We started with simple campus cleanup drives, but quickly realized the need for systemic change.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="relative">
          <img 
            src={campusImage} 
            alt="Air Force Institute of Technology campus" 
            class="rounded-lg shadow-xl w-full h-auto"
          />
          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 bg-green p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg max-w-xs">
            <p class="text-white font-medium italic">
              "Every piece of plastic we remove today is one less threat to tomorrow's Africa."
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission & Vision Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-cream-light to-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <SectionHeading 
        title="Our Purpose" 
        subtitle="Guided by clear goals and unwavering values"
        centered={true}
      />
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-12">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-dark mb-4">Mission Statement</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            To eliminate single-use plastics across Africa through education, innovation, and community action, while preserving our cultural heritage and promoting sustainable development.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-dark mb-4">Vision Statement</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            An Africa where communities thrive in harmony with nature, where traditional wisdom meets modern sustainability, and where future generations inherit clean waters and healthy ecosystems.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-dark mb-4">Short-Term Goals</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-green mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>- Educate students to properly dispose of their plastics.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-green mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>- Make sellers switch to using papers in place of plastics and students to buy snacks with a reusable bag.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-green mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>- Eco friendly AFIT.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-dark mb-4">Long-Term Goals</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-green mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
            </span>-Spread the movement to multiple uni's.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-green mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>- Get huge companies to switch from single use plastics to environmental friendly alternatives </span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-green mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>- Educate Nigerians through social media and make them aware of the dangers of the situation.</span>
            </li>
             <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-green mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>- Make Nigerians shop with reusable bag's</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

